snippet.title: Knockout City Season 6: City of Tomorrow - Arrives June 1st!
snippet.description:
Good morning, brawlers! It’s a new dawn in Knockout City, and we’ve never felt more “free.” If you’re new to the streets, then hey – you’re not gonna want to miss the latest and greatest in our next Season: it’s dodgebrawl down to its core, and it’s awesome!

City of Tomorrow arrives June 1st, but don't wait to join in on the fun! Play the Standard or Deluxe version before then, and you'll unlock the Loyalty Royalty bundle when Free to Play arrives. You'll score 2000 Holobux, Legendary Outfit, Gold Plated and a ton of extra goodies to help you seize the day, and some bonus XP!

The Loyalty Royalty Bonus contains:
- 2,000 Holobux
- 5 Style Chips
- 6-Pack of the new Season 6 Energy Drink
- Legendary Player Icon: Gold Plated Chonky
- Legendary Outfit: Gold Plated
- Legendary Taunt: Gold Plated WooHoo!
- Legendary Crew Banner: Gold Plated Pals
- Season 6 Match XP Boost
- Season 6 Crew XP Boost
- Season 6 Friend XP Boost

Read on for all the research you need in Season 6: https://www.ea.com/games/knockout-city/news/knockout-city-season-6-city-of-tomorrow
The City of Tomorrow’s just within our reach now, and on June 1st, we’ll be brawlin’ like there’s no tomorrow!
